name: MC LARS "Indie Rocket Science" CD
description: MC LARS "Indie Rocket Science" mixtape brings together underground indie rappers like Grieves, Sage Francis, MC Chris, MC Frontalot and more, including hip hop legend, KRS-ONE on the track "What is hip hop?"
